WEBVTT

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:30.240
will also not have pictures
of their family in their office.

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:36.496
They won't bring their family
to the company party.

00:09:36.520 --> 00:09:37.736
AG: During one project,

00:09:37.760 --> 00:09:40.696
Nancy met a firefighter
who was a strong segmentor.

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:44.976
NR: When he would go home after his shift,

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.656
he would wear flip-flops

00:09:46.680 --> 00:09:50.776
because he didn't want to wear
his firefighting boots

00:09:50.800 --> 00:09:53.216
and take them into his house.

00:09:53.240 --> 00:09:56.536
And what he also said is,
when he would get home

00:09:56.560 --> 00:09:59.696
he wouldn't touch
or hug his kids or his wife

00:09:59.720 --> 00:10:02.376
until he had taken a shower
and changed his clothes.